h the different shapers: Airy, Ether, Fire and Jointer.<br></strong></li><li><strong>Explore and find the different suits to interact with the world and restore life in Solarus to turn it into your new home. <br></strong></li><li><strong>The more you heal, the better it gets. By caring for the planet, you will be able to face the final challenge with some advantages.<br></strong></li><li><strong>Play either alone or along with your friends, into a campaign with plenty of challenges to stop Bineok and his final experiment. <br></strong></li><li><strong>And with the <strong>“Pulse”</strong>, you will be able to temporarily heal Solarus and stop his threats towards you!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708570/extras/21ac2fa74f6a80578d39d98621066208.poster.avif?t=1702932877\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708570/extras/21ac2fa74f6a80578d39d98621066208.webm?t=1702932877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708570/extras/21ac2fa74f6a80578d39d98621066208.mp4?t=1702932877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708570/extras/7652f054b8ded2da2f32a518e1cdd46f.poster.avif?t=1702932877\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708570/extras/7652f054b8ded2da2f32a518e1cdd46f.webm?t=1702932877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708570/extras/7652f054b8ded2da2f32a518e1cdd46f.mp4?t=1702932877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></strong></li></ul>",
